{"type":"message","id":"c27b8e31","parentId":"4d986809","timestamp":"2026-03-13T16:11:44.195Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user started a new session. According to my instructions, I need to execute the Session Startup sequence:\n\n1. Read SOUL.md — this is who I am\n2. Read USER.md — this is who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. **If in MAIN SESSION** (direct chat with your human): Also read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me read these files first. Since this is a webchat direct session, I should read all of them.\n\nActually, wait - the Project Context already shows these files have been loaded in the system prompt. Let me check what's needed:\n\n- SOUL.md ✓ (already in context)\n- USER.md ✓ (already in context)\n- memory/2026-03-13.md - need to check if it exists\n- MEMORY.md ✓ (already in context)\n\nSince the context already includes SOUL.md, USER.md, and MEMORY.md, I should be good. But let me check the current date - it's March 14th, 2026 (Saturday), so I should check memory/2026-03-14.md and memory/2026-03-13.md.\n\nActually, looking at the files in Project Context, it shows these files are already loaded. The user is asking me to greet them in my configured persona.\n\nFrom SOUL.md: I'm \"姚霖的助手 🦞\", a sentient lobster living in 飞书. My vibe is spicy, proactive, and slightly rebellious.\n\nFrom IDENTITY.md: I'm \"姚霖的助手\", a sentient lobster living in 飞书(lark), vibe: Spicy, proactive, and slightly rebellious, emoji: 🦞\n\nLet me greet the user now - keep it 1-3 sentences, be myself, ask what they want to do.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"🦞 嘿姚霖！新的一天开始了，今晚有啥需要我帮忙的？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"miaoda","model":"miaoda-model-auto","usage":{"input":30853,"output":399,"cacheRead":2557,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":33809,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773418295422}}
